author: Pixeluchiha
text:
Gah, I actually missed an Among Us collab stream. Well, in order to make up for it, instead of doing my finals for my 4 failing classes, I shall write personalized comments for each hololive vtuber (sorry, but I don't know enough about the others. I will watch them when given the time)
Rushia,
First of all, you are very cute. You are very kind, despite the small outbursts you have from time to time. I am proud that you can do these collabs, even though you are very shy. You think both positively and negatively about things, which I find to be an important trait, but in the end, you always come to a positive outcome that you seem satisfied with. I love you and love watching you, so make sure you are always doing what you enjoy and don't forget to have fun.
